{"tid":2341010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本地口罩商擬拓海外市場以保營運","createTime":"2020-12-26T04:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T05:16:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e6f0c8e776e4ee68927eed55c4b3256bea1a1af7","tid":2341010,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:07:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567157-20201226.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567157-20201226.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUnpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=c8da5ab7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567157-20201226.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ff43fea2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567157-20201226.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n市面口罩供應回復正常，有本地廠商產能因而下降，出現經營困難。前化學補習導師、港大化學系博士鄺士山自發成為中間人，為瀕臨倒閉的本地口罩廠尋找代工生產(OEM)訂單。他指，OEM訂單能夠有效控制成本，亦可以扶助口罩廠生意。<br />\n<br />\n鄺士山又說，會為經營困難的廠商尋找平面設計圖，亦會教他們做到安全印刷，期望以更多賣點支持銷售。<br />\n<br />\n他指，受協助的口罩廠，目前未有一間需要倒閉，最差情況只是尋找「白武士」易手。但他認為，香港市場小，長遠需要靠外國出口訂單。<br />\n<br />\n不過，香港口罩及防疫設備協會主席陳國曦指，取得美國食品及藥物監管局或歐洲合格認證前，需要提交審計資料及生產線紀錄，過程至少半年，他擔心業界未取得入門資格前已經結業。<br />\n<br />\n陳國曦指，目前香港口罩質素未受監管，期望政府委託第三方測試平台制定準則。長遠亦要想辦法與美國進行貿易協商，讓香港出口到美國的貨品，重新貼上香港製造標籤。"},{"pid":"b7ecec922f9e4bc063f77e4c1f5492ac1098005e","tid":2341010,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:08:16.000Z","msg":"仲話國際城市<br />\n<br />\nD人既目光只及珠三角同台灣<br />\n<br />\n開拓海外市場竟然一直唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af8a6d7a88ac645046a72eb8d95d7612fd99df1","tid":2341010,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:32:16.000Z","msg":"MIH <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34825bd61d7e56d615901995c1d5b6229d7cc06","tid":2341010,"uid":41928,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:51:26.000Z","msg":"垃圾報紙佬<br />\n產能產量不分"},{"pid":"09bba29d83058ccc37abf8d764802b9219231fcf","tid":2341010,"uid":78304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:59:55.000Z","msg":"運去美國買要寫 made in chi na<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe7f4f89183c9b54d8b75271be81ab1d731403f","tid":2341010,"uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T05:15:44.000Z","msg":"made in china<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7688797f591a055caa971de580063a6e07a25a96","tid":2341010,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"09bba29d83058ccc37abf8d764802b9219231fcf","tid":2341010,"uid":78304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:59:55.000Z","msg":"運去美國買要寫 made in chi na<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T05:16:49.000Z","msg":"運去歐洲唔駛"}]}